title: Irene
text: Agent Carly McGuire was so good at helping me find a better price on home and auto insurance. She saved me a lot of money, by her seeking the best policys for me. She also, was very personable with me and did a follow up call of getting me signed up with my last policy so that I did not loose auto insurance from one company to the one she found for me. I really do appreciate the great job. Sincerely, Irene Torres
